      h4 Thanks for stopping in. Let’s keep in touch!
      img.logo-andyou(src='/images/andyou-logo.svg')
      p Join our monthly newsletter designed to surface the collective expertise of our community.<br />We’d love for you to join! <i>We can’t be &yet without &you</i>.

